{"tid":1435339,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[農曆七月] 救起遇溺朋友 勇漢反魂斷南灣","createTime":"2019-08-09T04:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:47:16.000Z","uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8684513db8550ab27ccae9afe25944c5df1f3e","tid":1435339,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2045327/日報-港聞-救起遇溺朋友-勇漢反魂斷南灣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2045327%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%95%91%E8%B5%B7%E9%81%87%E6%BA%BA%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B-%E5%8B%87%E6%BC%A2%E5%8F%8D%E9%AD%82%E6%96%B7%E5%8D%97%E7%81%A3&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzbidffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=9b41b1bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2045327%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%95%91%E8%B5%B7%E9%81%87%E6%BA%BA%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B-%E5%8B%87%E6%BC%A2%E5%8F%8D%E9%AD%82%E6%96%B7%E5%8D%97%E7%81%A3&h=75ec437f\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2045327/日報-港聞-救起遇溺朋友-勇漢反魂斷南灣</a><br />\n星島日報 2019-08-09港聞</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/09/219929/i_1000x667_021105259.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F219929%2Fi_1000x667_021105259.jpg&h=85273797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(星島日報報道)一名中年漢，昨與友人駕乘兩艘機動小艇「遊船河」，將小艇停泊在港島南灣，聯袂下水暢泳，但一名青年遇溺呼救，他奮勇救起對方，自己卻體力不支遇溺下沉失蹤，消防蛙人花兩個小時，始將他尋獲，送院搶救但不治。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓石、四十九歲，昨日中午和五名友人遊船河，一行六人駕乘兩艘機動小艇，前往南灣對開二百米海面，進行水上活動。及至傍晚六時許，石與一名同行青年躍入水中暢泳，豈料該青年遇溺呼救，石奮勇上前把友人救起推回船上，惟他自己反而體力不支，未幾下沉海裏失蹤，同伴報警。<br />\n<br />\n水警輪和消防船趕抵現場，消防蛙入潛入水底搜索，由於天色漸黑，政府飛行服務隊直升機亦到場，在上空亮起照明燈協助搜救。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上八時三十分，消防蛙人在九米深水區尋獲事主，他上半身赤裸，僅穿上一條短褲，已無氣息，警方將他送到岸上，再急送醫院搶救，惜回天乏術，遺體稍後由仵工舁送殮房，以待剖屍檢驗。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，事主精於泳術，警方仍調查他遇溺原因。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n水鬼開工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9430a041b238e094a40def1195e3e92c78aa1f","tid":1435339,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"鬼掹腳"},{"pid":"8427b12713eaa9b465a055fe67ee15df2e70e648","tid":1435339,"uid":295650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca8684513db8550ab27ccae9afe25944c5df1f3e","tid":1435339,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2045327/日報-港聞-救起遇溺朋友-勇漢反魂斷南灣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2045327%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%95%91%E8%B5%B7%E9%81%87%E6%BA%BA%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B-%E5%8B%87%E6%BC%A2%E5%8F%8D%E9%AD%82%E6%96%B7%E5%8D%97%E7%81%A3&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzbidffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=9b41b1bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2045327%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%95%91%E8%B5%B7%E9%81%87%E6%BA%BA%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B-%E5%8B%87%E6%BC%A2%E5%8F%8D%E9%AD%82%E6%96%B7%E5%8D%97%E7%81%A3&h=75ec437f\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/2045327/日報-港聞-救起遇溺朋友-勇漢反魂斷南灣</a><br />\n星島日報 2019-08-09港聞</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/08/09/219929/i_1000x667_021105259.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F219929%2Fi_1000x667_021105259.jpg&h=85273797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(星島日報報道)一名中年漢，昨與友人駕乘兩艘機動小艇「遊船河」，將小艇停泊在港島南灣，聯袂下水暢泳，但一名青年遇溺呼救，他奮勇救起對方，自己卻體力不支遇溺下沉失蹤，消防蛙人花兩個小時，始將他尋獲，送院搶救但不治。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓石、四十九歲，昨日中午和五名友人遊船河，一行六人駕乘兩艘機動小艇，前往南灣對開二百米海面，進行水上活動。及至傍晚六時許，石與一名同行青年躍入水中暢泳，豈料該青